<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Payment Failed - {{eventTitle}}</title>
</head>
<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f7fa;">
    
    <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="background-color: #f4f7fa; padding: 40px 20px;">
        <tr>
            <td align="center">
                <table width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 16px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
                    
                    <!-- Header -->
                    <tr>
                        <td style="background-color: #dc3545; padding: 50px 40px; text-align: center;">
                            <h1 style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #ffffff; font-size: 32px; font-weight: 700;">⚠️ Payment Failed</h1>
                            <p style="margin: 0; color: #ffffff; font-size: 18px; opacity: 0.9;">We couldn't process your payment</p>
                        </td>
                    </tr>

                    <!-- Content -->
                    <tr>
                        <td style="padding: 45px 40px;">
                            
                            <p style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-size: 18px; color: #1a1a1a; line-height: 1.6;">
                                Hi <strong style="color: #dc3545;">{{userName}}</strong>,
                            </p>
                            <p style="margin: 0 0 35px 0; font-size: 16px; color: #555555; line-height: 1.7;">
                                Unfortunately, we were unable to process your payment for tickets to <strong>{{eventTitle}}</strong>. But don't worry — your tickets are still available!
                            </p>

                            <!-- Error Details -->
                            <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="background-color: #f8d7da; border-left: 5px solid #dc3545; border-radius: 10px; margin-bottom: 35px;">
                                <tr>
                                    <td style="padding: 28px;">
                                        <h3 style="margin: 0 0 18px 0; font-size: 20px; color: #721c24; font-weight: 700;">Transaction Details</h3>
                                        
                                        <table width="100%" cellpadding="10" cellspacing="0" border="0">
                                            <tr>
                                                <td style="font-size: 15px; color: #721c24; font-weight: 700; width: 130px;">Reference:</td>
                                                <td style="font-size: 14px; color: #721c24; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;">{{reference}}</td>
                                            </tr>
                                            <tr>
                                                <td style="font-size: 15px; color: #721c24; font-weight: 700; vertical-align: top;">Reason:</td>
                                                <td style="font-size: 15px; color: #721c24; line-height: 1.6;">{{reason}}</td>
                                            </tr>
                                        </table>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                            </table>

                            <!-- Troubleshooting Steps -->
                            <h3 style="margin: 0 0 25px 0; font-size: 22px; color: #1a1a1a; font-weight: 700;">How to Fix This</h3>
                            
                            <!-- Step 1 -->
                            <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="background-color: #f9fafb; border-radius: 10px; margin-bottom: 15px; border: 1px solid #e1e8ed;">
                                <tr>
                                    <td style="padding: 22px; vertical-align: top; width: 55px;">
                                        <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: #ffffff; width: 38px; height: 38px; border-radius: 50%; text-align: center; line-height: 38px; font-weight: 800; font-size: 18px;">1</div>
                                    </td>
                                    <td style="padding: 22px 22px 22px 0;">
                                        <p style="margin: 0 0 5px 0; font-size: 16px; color: #1a1a1a; font-weight: 700;">Check your card details</p>
                                        <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #666666; line-height: 1.6;">Verify your card number, expiry date, and CVV are correct</p>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                            </table>

                            <!-- Step 2 -->
                            <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="background-color: #f9fafb; border-radius: 10px; margin-bottom: 15px; border: 1px solid #e1e8ed;">
                                <tr>
                                    <td style="padding: 22px; vertical-align: top; width: 55px;">
                                        <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: #ffffff; width: 38px; height: 38px; border-radius: 50%; text-align: center; line-height: 38px; font-weight: 800; font-size: 18px;">2</div>
                                    </td>
                                    <td style="padding: 22px 22px 22px 0;">
                                        <p style="margin: 0 0 5px 0; font-size: 16px; color: #1a1a1a; font-weight: 700;">Verify sufficient funds</p>
                                        <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #666666; line-height: 1.6;">Ensure you have enough balance in your account</p>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                            </table>

                            <!-- Step 3 -->
                            <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="background-color: #f9fafb; border-radius: 10px; margin-bottom: 15px; border: 1px solid #e1e8ed;">
                                <tr>
                                    <td style="padding: 22px; vertical-align: top; width: 55px;">
                                        <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: #ffffff; width: 38px; height: 38px; border-radius: 50%; text-align: center; line-height: 38px; font-weight: 800; font-size: 18px;">3</div>
                                    </td>
                                    <td style="padding: 22px 22px 22px 0;">
                                        <p style="margin: 0 0 5px 0; font-size: 16px; color: #1a1a1a; font-weight: 700;">Try a different payment method</p>
                                        <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #666666; line-height: 1.6;">Use another card or select bank transfer</p>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                            </table>

                            <!-- Step 4 -->
                            <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="background-color: #f9fafb; border-radius: 10px; margin-bottom: 35px; border: 1px solid #e1e8ed;">
                                <tr>
                                    <td style="padding: 22px; vertical-align: top; width: 55px;">
                                        <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: #ffffff; width: 38px; height: 38px; border-radius: 50%; text-align: center; line-height: 38px; font-weight: 800; font-size: 18px;">4</div>
                                    </td>
                                    <td style="padding: 22px 22px 22px 0;">
                                        <p style="margin: 0 0 5px 0; font-size: 16px; color: #1a1a1a; font-weight: 700;">Contact your bank</p>
                                        <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #666666; line-height: 1.6;">Your bank may have declined the transaction for security reasons</p>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                            </table>

                            <!-- Reassurance Banner -->
                            <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="background-color: #e7f3ff; border-left: 5px solid #0066cc; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 35px;">
                                <tr>
                                    <td style="padding: 25px 28px;">
                                        <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 15px; color: #004085; line-height: 1.7;">
                                            <strong>Don't worry!</strong> Your tickets are still available and haven't been sold to anyone else. You can try purchasing again at any time.
                                        </p>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                            </table>

                            <!-- CTA Button -->
                            <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
                                <tr>
                                    <td align="center" style="padding: 25px 0;">
                                        <a href="{{retryLink}}" style="display: inline-block; background-color: #28a745; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; padding: 17px 55px; border-radius: 35px; font-size: 17px; font-weight: 700; box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(40, 167, 69, 0.4);">Try Again Now</a>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                            </table>

                            <p style="margin: 25px 0 0 0; font-size: 14px; color: #888888; text-align: center; line-height: 1.6;">
                                Still having issues? We're here to help!<br>
                                Contact <a href="mailto:support@eventful.com" style="color: #667eea; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;">support@eventful.com</a> or call +234 800 000 0000
                            </p>
                            
                        </td>
                    </tr>

                    <!-- Footer -->
                    <tr>
                        <td style="background-color: #f9fafb; padding: 35px 40px; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid #e1e8ed;">
                            <p style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #555555;">
                                Need assistance? We're here to help!
                            </p>
                            <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 12px; color: #999999;">
                                © {{year}} Eventful. All rights reserved.
                            </p>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    
</body>
</html>
